        <scopecontent id="ref2">
            <head>Scope and Contents note</head>
            <p>One certificate, dated May 17, 1894, stating that Morris Patterson Harris has contributed five dollars toward the erection of the Nathan Hale Memorial in Huntington, Long Island.</p>
        </scopecontent>
